&lt;li&gt;Refine and standardize processes, policies, and workflows to scale working with GTM leadership and functional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive continual assessment of existing sales processes to deliver operational excellence through iterative improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be accountable for the end-to-end operational infrastructure, overseeing the selection and implementation of tools and technologies to support GTM and revenue operations, including CRM systems (Salesforce) and related sales tools (Gong, Loopio, SPIFF etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive system consolidation, migration, and implementation projects that improve data quality, reduce operational friction, and unlock new capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
