&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a seasoned Senior Manager to lead two critical and complementary functions within Business Technology: IT Product Management and IT Software Asset Management. This is a high-impact leadership role responsible for bridging the gap between Business Technology (BT) capabilities and business needs — ensuring internal technology systems are managed with product rigor and adopted effectively across the organization. You will directly manage a team of Business Technology Product Managers and Asset Management Lead/Specialists, bringing structure, strategic alignment, and operational excellence to both disciplines. This role reports to the Head of Business Technology.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We work &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.marqeta.com/blog/2022/05/10/flexible-first&quot;&gt;Flexible First&lt;/a&gt;. This role can be performed remotely anywhere within Ontario or British Columbia, Canada. We’d love for you to join us!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is both for an existing and non-existing vacancy.&lt;/p&gt;
