&lt;li&gt;Partner with BT Strategy &amp;amp; Operations to establish product governance mechanisms including Steering Committees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organizational Change Management (OCM)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
